snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 04 - Kuroda Miyuki (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 4: Kuroda Miyuki is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1997.
